{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/JS-bit-operator/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Discreater Blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"1d7a37fb-a71a-5d49-a414-b4b8958afe88","excerpt":"最近刷leetcode的时候，碰到要处理上边界($2^{31}-1$)和下边界($-2^{31}$)的情况，这时候想当然地用了移位操作符来计算2的幂次，本以为js的number类型上限应该大于32位，但是实际情况并不是和想象中的一样，先看结果： 1左移31位变成了负数，出现这种情况是因为js…","html":"<p>最近刷leetcode的时候，碰到要处理<code class=\"language-text\">int</code>上边界($2^{31}-1$)和下边界($-2^{31}$)的情况，这时候想当然地用了移位操作符<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;&lt;</code>来计算2的幂次，本以为js的number类型上限应该大于32位，但是实际情况并不是和想象中的一样，先看结果：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">31</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2147483648</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// -2^31</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">30</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">1073741824</span>  <span class=\"token comment\">// 2^30</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">31</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2147483648</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">31</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">2147483648</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token number\">32</span>\n<span class=\"token number\">1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>1左移31位变成了负数，出现这种情况是因为js的按位操作符是<strong>将操作数看作32位来计算</strong>，结果也是32位的形式。\n下面是<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/Bitwise_Operators#Summary\">MDN的官方解释</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>按位操作符（Bitwise operators）</strong> 将其操作数（operands）当作32位的比特序列（由0和1组成），而不是十进制、十六进制或八进制数值。例如，十进制数9，用二进制表示则为1001。按位操作符操作数字的二进制形式，但是返回值依然是标准的JavaScript数值。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>顺便推荐一波<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/27662366\">进阶的解决办法</a>，来自知乎的ice1000</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"JS 按位操作符溢出问题","date":"2020-03-14"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/JS-bit-operator/","previous":null,"next":null}}}